<%content_for :title do%>How It Works<%end%>
<h1>How It Works</h1>
<br>
<ul id="how_it_works_list" class="list-group">
	<li class="list-group-item">
		<h4 class="list-group-item-heading hiw_list_heading">Sign Up</h4>
		Sign up and pay $25 or more to be entered in the ICYF college basketball bracket challenge.
	</li>
	<li class="list-group-item">
		<h4 class="list-group-item-heading hiw_list_heading">Invite your friends</h4>
		Let your friends, family and co-workers know to sign up.  Sure, they will probably make better picks than you, but hey, this is for charity.
	</li>
	<li class="list-group-item">
		<h4 class="list-group-item-heading hiw_list_heading">Make your picks</h4>
		Upon sign in, you will be taken directly to your personal college basketball tournament bracket.  If the pairings are out, you can make your picks and save your bracket.
	</li>
	<li class="list-group-item">
		<h4 class="list-group-item-heading hiw_list_heading">Check the standings</h4>
		Once the college basketball tournament begins, standings and bracket results will be updated after every game.  Check in frequently to see how you are doing against the rest of the field.  <a href="/scoring">Check out how your bracket is scored here.</a>
	</li>
	<li class="list-group-item">
		<h4 class="list-group-item-heading hiw_list_heading">Crown the winner!</h4>
		After the college basketball tournament is complete the top 5 place winners will receive some super awesome prizes.
	</li>
</ul>


